description:
I am open to feelings and it can be painful.
 
When you are vulnerable, it enriches your life, 
but if something suddenly goes wrong, 
it can be quite excruciating. 

On the other hand, if you do not open your heart to people, 
you risk ending your days alone, far from the whole world.

You can always close your eyes to what you see, 
but you cannot close your heart to what you feel.
